    "Use `mpv' with `youtube-dl' to open URLs, asking for desired quality
Documentation: https://github.com/ytdl-org/youtube-dl#format-selection"
    (let ((quality-arg "")
          (quality-val (completing-read "Max height resolution (0 for unlimited): "
